# sphinx_null_theme

![Code style Prettier badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/codestyle-Prettier-blue?labelColor=097cba&color=163B36)

## About This Project

This project is a weird Sphinx theme with no appereance but functionaly only. Intented to be used as parent theme by other [ReadCraft themes](https://readcraft.io).
